{"tid":1880112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深井豪景花園29隻動物疑遭人高處擲下15隻死亡","createTime":"2020-02-14T15:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T15:36:38.000Z","uid":6103,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fee628a8279ac4ee401a9e214e7d4b43c421c011","tid":1880112,"uid":6103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:08:56.000Z","msg":"深井豪景花園29隻動物疑遭人高處擲下15隻死亡<br />\n14.02.2020 22:42<br />\n<br />\n深井豪景花園發生殘酷對待動物案，共29隻動物懷疑被人由高處擲下，其中15隻死亡，愛護動物協會人員到場，發現9隻寵物鼠及5隻花貓仍然生存，但都奄奄一息，檢走交獸醫檢查及治療，死去的動物交由漁護署解剖或化驗。<br />\n<br />\n事發在下午2時許，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">這批動物包括寵物鼠、兔子、花貓及雀鳥等</span></span>，被發現倒臥在豪景花園19座對開山坡，保安員報警。警方到場調查，發現過半數動物已死亡，翻查現場閉路電視片段後，相信動物是被人由高處擲下，暫時未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死仆街"},{"pid":"c544fd6a3de54ab49861d35f3783c2604b937065","tid":1880112,"uid":73111,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:09:37.000Z","msg":"高處擲下雀鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30fc7c0b0833c9fd933f43d8b5fe256bb096aca","tid":1880112,"uid":132587,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/15/125956_0753c398284fca1ec65eb57167117113.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F15%2F125956_0753c398284fca1ec65eb57167117113.gif&h=2ba60e66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔該搵人擲個垃圾主人落埋去"},{"pid":"e37afbac860b24776d0d2ed2ab181f340b407376","tid":1880112,"uid":304856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c544fd6a3de54ab49861d35f3783c2604b937065","tid":1880112,"uid":73111,"like":3,"disl